    "original_title": "Brooklyn: Atlantic Avenue - Montauk Avenue",
    "text": "(1)\nAtlantic Ave., looking east from, but not including Montauk Ave. The view shows the tracks of the Long Island Railroad. On the right, is shown part of No. 3276 Atlantic Ave., a frame house.\nJuly 27, 1930.\nP. L. Sperr.\n\n(2)\nThe same, from Berrian Street. The tracks are not clearly seen in this view.\nJuly 27, 1930.\nP. L. Sperr.\n\n(3)\nThe same, from Berrian Street, showing the tracks more clearly.\nJuly 27, 1930.\nP. L. Sperr.\n",
